          <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align: left;">Why We Started Ayvant</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-600" style="margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.8;">We've all been there – stuck on hold with IT support, listening to someone read from a script who clearly doesn't understand (or care about) your actual problem. We started Ayvant because we believed there had to be a better way.</p>
          <p class="text-zinc-600" style="margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.8;">Our founders spent years working in IT for large corporations before realizing that small and medium-sized businesses deserved the same level of expertise and attention – but with a personal touch.</p>
          <p class="text-zinc-600" style="line-height: 1.8;">Today, we're proud to serve dozens of law firms, accounting practices, and professional service businesses across Vancouver and the Lower Mainland. We've built our reputation on doing what we say we'll do, explaining things clearly, and being there when you need us.</p>
